==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: News-writer
<hw>News"-writ`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who gathers
news for, and writes, news-letters, articles in news periodicals, or
items for broadcast on news programs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

